item.title: Story 3: The All-Powerful Princess Lucy
item.description: It has been years since I have conquered this domain. These servants have been doing well but I still cannot understand why they keep standing on two legs. Are they always scared? Well, that is to be expected. Oh yes, it is very hard being me every morning when I wake up with my servants still lying in bed. How could they? isn’t it that a proper servant should wake up before their master?
